## CameraManager.releaseCameraList() method

释放获取到的摄像头信息列表,该接口仅释放摄像头信息但不会关闭已打开的摄像头,调用该接口后XRCameraHandle依然可用于getSupportedConfigList/open/close

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
static releaseCameraList( list : Camera []) : void ;
```

|  --- | --- | --- |
|  list | [Camera](./extractor.camera.md) \[\] | 摄像头列表 |

<b>Returns:</b>

void
